dct_title_s: Manila, P.I., plan of proposed improvements
dct_description_sm: approved June 28, 1905 by D.H. Burnham, Pierce Anderson.
Shows present buildings, future building sites, block numbers, and selected buildings.
Oriented with north to the upper left.
"This plan accompanies report to Hon. William H. Taft, Secy. of War."
